{"type": "article", "id": 38048, "title": "加拿大鹅计划年底上市，以及，这里有YEEZY最新款发售店铺一览 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-02-22T03:23:36Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1782, "name": "Coach"}, {"id": 8634, "name": "Supreme"}, {"id": 24719, "name": "Yeezy Boost"}, {"id": 35943, "name": "加拿大鹅"}, {"id": 36104, "name": "Spectacles"}, {"id": 2636, "name": "Swatch"}, {"id": 5963, "name": "Snap"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 35, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170222100250bXInau9GjZ5tRPBr.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.cpp-luxury.com/swatch-group-to-raise-u-k-prices-by-5-percent/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Swatch 集团要在英国提价 5%</b></a> | 据最近的 WatchPro 报道，瑞士手表集团 Swatch 将从今年的 3 月 1 日起，把旗下的至少六个品牌的手表在英国的售价提升 5%。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/canada-goose-filed-prospectus-for-ipo-initial-public-offering-10812900/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>加拿大鹅已提交 IPO 招股说明书，将于年底完成上市</b></a> | 说明书透露，在截至去年 3 月 31 日的年度中，集团净销售额为 2.9 亿美元，净利润为 2650 万美元，毛利率为 50.1%。贝恩资本已于 2013 年 12 月收购了 Canada Goose 70% 的股权，此次公开发股约占用 10% 的股份，贝恩仍有对 Canada Goose 的绝对控制权。</p><p><a href=\"http://www.cpp-luxury.com/coach-opens-in-milan-first-store-in-italy/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Coach 在意大利开首家独立门店</b></a> | 前不久，Coach 在意大利米兰的奢侈品商圈 Via Montenapoleone，开设了它在意大利的首家店铺。该店占地 1650 平方米，由 Coach 的创意总监 Stuart Vevers，与设计工作室 Studio Sofield 联合设计。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222104842cPQ5WBuh9FCqDpMj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/02/20/snapchat-spectacles-buy-price/#slide-4\" rel=\"nofollow\">Snap 推出的能够拍摄 10 秒短视频的智能太阳眼镜 Spectacles</a>，现在可以于 Spectacles 的官网买到了。定价仍然是 129.99 美元，仅限美国地区发售，并且每个家庭限购 6 副。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017022210033332HRbeAik0q9MjKS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222100333GmTwN125VfJnbaXZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222100342tA4VdI8l5rBs0LQx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222100342XtJcIBoi2wMTmAzq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>位于新泽西的球鞋名店 Packer Shoes，找来了 Reebok 携手推出了<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/2/doraemon-packer-shoes-reebok-instapump-fury\" rel=\"nofollow\">以多啦 A 梦为主题的特别款 Instapump Fury</a>。这双鞋的鞋身以多啦 A 梦象征性的天蓝色为底色，辅以白色点缀，原来的 Pump 按钮也换成了叮当的图案。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222100411E3y9KJHqfBQ1tVUb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702221004219Mh7kL4P1GXquHbJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222100429R6PFz4EteWuw5ATG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>2 月 21 日至 2 月 22 日，日本潮牌 Human Made 与 AKB48 的团员小嶋阳菜合作，在东京涩谷区神宫前的  ラフォーレ原宿，推出<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/2/human-made-x-akb48\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Store by Nyan</a> 两日限定快闪店。店铺限定的商品包括  Souvenir Jacket、 T-Shirt、手机壳和水杯。 </p><p></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222100514KYo2Jpx1gVSAh3Oz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222100514v9o0IiyZ5RQTOGSh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222100525417vHWfbD8NXhmyj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222100525f2TC307SVR19v6we.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222100538TRUjvaNdXg1tnkbh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222100538ewGEYusR9difJAlc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222100538Ffn6BL9iqc4rh3Kw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222100549GpghwY2HAdyQlU7W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>这一季的优衣库 <a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/2/futura-x-uniqlo-ut-collection-preview\" rel=\"nofollow\">UT，找来了传奇涂鸦艺术家 Futura 合作</a>。该系列包括 12 款不同的 UT 设计，其中有 6 款童装尺寸，定价为 990 日元，将于三月全球同步推出。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222100636ivBXFk962WjAHLhQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222100636KudUS9ECbcsVr1RH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222100636JAOPiR2V6hEmz0xq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702221006366yKAsP9taEhfTV4R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222100648LcMp79H13CNa6bgP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222100647F12yTQYUh9spOWJS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222100647ewF7QlBzU6JTavd8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222100648iyBd1DEFN2LcpZbv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222100648n6PHWfCdX4hr3pRJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222100648xbNi2MHPDtkql6Zm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702221006486laWrPSBAf4tITqF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222100648LqT37FSdykUn1jQG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/02/20/supreme-metrocards/\" rel=\"nofollow\">纽约地铁官方之前通过 Twitter 宣布将在 Times Square 和 Broadway Lafayette 等指定站点发售 Supreme 地铁卡</a>，并且不再需要 75 美元，而是可以通过充值任意数目来购买。随后，大批的 Supreme 粉丝涌入，在纽约地铁站内的引起混乱。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222100831XOVAI437r5qE0xK1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>全新的 YEEZY BOOST 350 V2 “斑马”配色版将于 2 月 25 日登场。今天起，已经可以通过  adidas Confirmed app 登记预定。 </p><p>从日前公布的发售店铺具体信息来看，大中华区只在上海南京西路及香港铜锣湾京士顿街两家旗舰店有售。查看完整的店铺列表，请看<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/02/21/adidas-yeezy-boost-350-v2-zebra-store-list/\" rel=\"nofollow\">这里</a>。 </p><p></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222100929EkGVLiJdjvQ1c5al.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222100929yuIjlQZRa5K3FdkL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222100937q9m6eX57MfstxPJO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222100937b1hSWM9mPdxtauYk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222100937N0wTh2CHkomzGita.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222100943PKpSfkJCiqEOsaD5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p><p class=\"\">题图来自：<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/02/20/supreme-metrocards/\" rel=\"nofollow\">highsnobiety</a></p>"}